## Implemented Phases

### Phase 1: Infrastructure ✅
- [ApiResponse.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/ApiResponse.php) - Standardized API responses
- [RoleMiddleware.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/RoleMiddleware.php) - 5 new RBAC methods
- `audit_logs` table - Activity logging

### Phase 2: Admin Module ✅
| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `/admin/users` | GET | List all users |
| `/admin/users/{id}` | GET | Get single user |
| `/admin/users/{id}` | PUT | Update user |
| `/admin/users/import` | POST | Bulk CSV import |
| `/admin/courses` | GET/POST | Course CRUD |
| `/admin/classes` | GET/POST | Class CRUD |
| `/admin/classes/{id}/enroll` | POST | Enroll student |
| `/admin/classes/{id}/assign-teacher` | POST | Assign teacher |
| `/admin/students/import` | POST | Bulk student import |

### Phase 3: Teacher Module ✅
| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `/teacher/dashboard` | GET | Dashboard data |
| `/teacher/classes` | GET | My assigned classes |
| `/teacher/classes/{id}/students` | GET | Students in class |
| `/teacher/attendance/mark` | POST | Mark attendance |
| `/teacher/attendance/{classId}` | GET | View attendance |
| `/teacher/attendance/import` | POST | Bulk attendance import |
| `/teacher/schedule` | GET | My timetable |

### Phase 4: Student Module ✅
| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `/student/dashboard` | GET | Dashboard data |
| `/student/profile` | GET/PUT | Profile management |
| `/student/attendance` | GET | My attendance |
| `/student/timetable` | GET | My schedule |
| `/student/grades` | GET | My grades |
| `/student/notifications` | GET | My notifications |

### Phase 5: Employee Module ✅
| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `/employee/dashboard` | GET | Dashboard with leave balance |
| `/employee/profile` | GET/PUT | Profile management |
| `/employee/attendance` | GET | My attendance records |

